  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to DeviceKit-power</title>

    <para>The <application>DeviceKit-power</application> provides an interface
    to enumerate power sources on the system and control system-wide power
    management.</para>

    &lfs65_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&DeviceKit-power-download-http;"/></para>
      </listitem>
